metadata.name: Pepe Checks Encased
metadata.description: Woke up to a timeline full of Checks and Pepe's. Couldn't resist in creating something that may or may not be notable. Encased in glass, it has to be notable right? Thank you Jack Butcher and Vincent Van Dough for the inspiration and entertainment. Mint or don't mint. I'm not here to force you. It's free. Come along on wherever this journey goes or don't.
